{"result": {"folders": ["ucore_plus", "other"], "nr": 805, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2016-04-17T23:37:05Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6ry30g7v1z", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-17T23:37:05Z", "data": "in57pih42271yh", "type": "create"}, {"to": "in57pih2pf51yg", "uid": "im5xso4yv3Q", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-26T08:57:42Z", "data": "inh799oa7vp6ao", "type": "s_answer"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "i6ry30g7v1z", "subject": "缓存相关的问题", "created": "2016-04-17T23:37:05Z", "content": "<p>在阅读一些OS源码的时候&#xff0c;经常遇到一些问题&#xff0c;感到很困惑&#xff0c;所以想请教一下各位老师同学与网友们。</p>\n<p>有时会在结构体末尾看到&#xff1a;</p>\n<p>#define CACHE_LINE_SIZE  128</p>\n<pre>__aligned(CACHE_LINE_SIZE) </pre>\n<p>例如&#xff1a;</p>\n<pre>struct percpu {<br /> struct proc *__current;  <br /> int apic_id;   <br /> uintptr_t self;   <br /> struct percpu_sched sched;<br />} __aligned(CACHE_LINE_SIZE);</pre>\n<p>但是绝大多数的结构体并没有发现CACHE_LINE_SIZE大小对齐。</p>\n<p>在何种情况下需要用cache line&#xff1f;</p>\n<p></p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["other", "student", "ucore_plus"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 118, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2016-04-26T08:57:42Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [{"role": "student", "name": "再度燃烧", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": "1425340926_35.png", "id": "i6ry30g7v1z", "photo_url": "https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/photos/i6ry30g7v1z/1425340926_35.png", "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "inh799o7t236an", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "im5xso4yv3Q", "subject": "", "created": "2016-04-26T08:57:42Z", "content": "<p>这个缓冲行的大小估计跟&#xff08;CACHE&#xff09;硬件有关&#xff0c;为了好管理&#xff0c;故会这样设置。这只是一种猜测</p>"}], "type": "s_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": ["i6ry30g7v1z"], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "in57pih2pf51yg", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": n